node.text: So many layers. Wow. 🤤. That dosa thiripi for turning sandwich 👏👏👏

Its #sudasuda #varikoadu sandwich & everyone at home had it #madamada &  it got finished #gadagada in no time.
#latergram 
Not a detailed recipe but here is a summary.Followed these steps & #ellathayum #nanna #ammukki toasted with butter..
First layer :
📌Hung curd + honey + chia seeds
📌Mushrooms sauteed in butter
📌Homemade pickled cucumber - it has apple cider vinegar, fresh turmeric, brown sugar,& cloves
📌Tomatoes
Second layer
📌Mint coriander chutney - standard green chutney
📌Oven dried cherry tomatoes marinated in olive oil + italian herbs + salt
📌Oven dried onion garlic powder
📌Grated cheese ( I don't remember which cheese I used..)
📌Pickled onions (same like cucumber above)
Most importantly you need BREAD #mylaard 😀
